{"tid":2414330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲法律系校花「50人斬成就」投身拍AV竟是這原因！","createTime":"2021-02-19T10:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T10:59:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"369af3cab40e68ff3fa1adda108b29bca76b3966","tid":2414330,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"日本現年25歲的AV女優結城留美奈（結城るみな），她不但擁有相當甜美優異的外型，還出身自名校法律系，一出道馬上受到大家的目光，更有不少人好奇，她為何放棄高薪的律師產業，反而投身成人業界，對此，她直接了當地回答：「就是很喜歡愛愛」讓不少人相當驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3032121-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3032121-PH.jpg&h=426f31d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲結城留美奈有著甜美優異的外型，更出身於名校法律系。（圖／翻攝自結城留美奈推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3032126-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3032126-PH.jpg&h=6b54245b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲結城留美奈曾參加過大學選美得冠軍，卻投身於AV產業。（圖／翻攝自結城留美奈推特）<br />\n<br />\n結城留美奈原本就讀名校法律系，大學時期甚至獲得校內選美比賽冠軍，然而畢業後卻轉換跑道進入AV界，許多人好奇想知道背後原因。而結城留美奈參加深夜綜藝節目時，直接爆出真相，原來她「就是很喜歡愛愛」及「享受被人關注的目光」等，讓現場來賓驚呼不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3032133-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3032133-PH.jpg&h=81a6c476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼結城留美奈描述自己出道原因後，讓現場來賓與觀眾驚訝不已。（圖／翻攝自結城留美奈推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3032137-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3032137-PH.jpg&h=317fb7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，結城留美奈私下也曾有50位性經驗的對象，可見她對於兩性敦倫有著一定程度喜愛。而根據《週刊文春》報導，結城留美奈不諱言入行也是為「向前男友復仇」，她還解釋「分手後異性關係較為自由，自然爆發，所以決定當AV女優。」造成話題。"},{"pid":"89cdc8ce1d0c7009951cd9fc8d9697d72b25ceff","tid":2414330,"uid":261849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"最後個張圖3個都咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0349489ea2c654efaf4bf20b325b198613ed6ce5","tid":2414330,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"嚇撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bb31410fcca8f6de376907158aa58f85610989","tid":2414330,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89cdc8ce1d0c7009951cd9fc8d9697d72b25ceff","tid":2414330,"uid":261849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"最後個張圖3個都咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"遠近鏡既問題"},{"pid":"0553bbc86c957fe051576c8d33ac3bb471406847","tid":2414330,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89cdc8ce1d0c7009951cd9fc8d9697d72b25ceff","tid":2414330,"uid":261849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"最後個張圖3個都咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"中間果件肥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab6f8146a1f470dbea2506469e4e9a17e4c6bb1","tid":2414330,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0553bbc86c957fe051576c8d33ac3bb471406847","tid":2414330,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89cdc8ce1d0c7009951cd9fc8d9697d72b25ceff","tid":2414330,"uid":261849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:1